values.description: The customer's bank account has insufficient funds.

values.description: The customer's bank cannot process the charge.

values.description: The customer's bank cannot proceed with the debit since it has not been authorized.

values.name: CUSTOMER_INITIATED
values.description: The customer initiated the dispute, so you should contact the customer for additional details to find out why the payment was disputed.
